# Visual Style Rules

## Retro Green Aesthetic
- ALWAYS use a retro, terminal/CRT-style green color scheme for all visual elements
- Primary green color: #00ff00 or #0f0 (bright terminal green)
- Background: #000 (black)
- Use monospace fonts (Courier New, monospace, or similar retro terminal fonts)
- Add green glow effects (text-shadow, box-shadow with green)
- Maintain retro/80s terminal aesthetic in all UI elements
- All text, borders, and visual effects should use green (#00ff00, #0f0, or variations)
- Avoid modern flat design - prefer retro CRT/terminal styling

